<p>Hello <%= @freelancer.name %>,</p>

<p>
  You have successfully submitted changes for the task "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>".
</p>

<h3>Task Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Task ID:</strong> <%= @task.id %></li>
  <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @task.title %></li>
  <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> <%= @task.deadline ? @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") : "Not set" %></li>
  <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @task.status.capitalize %></li>
</ul>

<p>
  The client (<strong><%= @task.client.name %></strong>) has been notified of your submitted changes. If any additional revisions are needed, the client will communicate with you directly via Gighive.
</p>

<p>
  You can view the task details and monitor the client's feedback here:
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to 'View Task on Gighive', task_url(@task), style: 'color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none;' %>
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for your dedication and professionalism. Keep up the great work!
</p>

<p>
  Best Regards,<br>
  <strong>The Gighive Team</strong>
</p>
